      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atdarrajt man tahs Taif- \nnibas Wahrtis/ ka es zaur tahm \neetm/ un tam KUNGAAM pa- \nteizu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schahs irr ta KUNGA \nWahrtis/ zaur ko tee Taifnee \nce-ees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es pateizu teiw/ ka tu \nmann efi paklautijs/ un man \npar Pestifschanu bijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Akmins/ ko tee Nam- \nma-darritaji atmettuschi/ irr par \nStuhru-Akmint tappis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas irr no ta KUNGA/ \nun irr Brihnums muhfäs Azzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schi irr ta Deena/ ko \ntas KUNGS irr darrijs/ pree- \nzafimees un lihgimostimees eekich \ntahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak KUNGS! palihds \nnu/ ak KUNGS! lai labbi is- \ndohdahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Slawehts lai irr/ kas \nnahe ta KUNGA Wahrdá/ \nmehs twehtijam juhs no ta KUN- \nGA Namma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS irr par \nSTIPRU DEEWU/ kas \nmuhs apguifmo/ peeeneet tohs \nSwehtku ( Uppurus ) ar Sat- \ntehm/ lihds ta Altara Raggeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu efi mans STIP- \nRAJS DEEWS/ un es pa- \nteizu teiw/ mans Deews// es pa- \naugstinafschu teiw.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pateizceet tam KUN- \nGA/ wiꞥſch irr labs/ jo\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta CXIX. Dseefma.\nJrr weena garra Mahzischanas Dseefma/ \nmums Deewa Wahrdü apraksta un f \nteis ir luhds/ ka Deewssaur to paschum \ngribbetu apskaidroht/ ka mehs to/ kam \nmehs dshwojam mihti turram/ lapr \ndsirdam/ nofirscbu pahrdohmajam/ un \nwenam Gaischumam us muhfeem Zett \npakkat eetam/ un pehz ta dshwojam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wehtigee irr tee/kas \nnenoseedsigeim Zette \nWeet/ kas eekch ta KU \nGA Bauslibas staiga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Swehtigee irr/ kas win \nLeezibas turr: Kas no wif \nSir̃ds winan mekle.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir Netaisnibu ne darre \nneds statga us winna Zetteem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu efi pawehlejs/ ka \nwus Bauslus buhs tohti fo \ngaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kaut manni Zelfius to we \ndsihtohs/ tawus Eikumus fo \ngaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad es us wisfeem tawee \nBausleem raundsichu/ tad ne ta \nschu es Kauna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es pateikchu teiw ar sk \ndru Sir̃di/ kad es buhschu t \nwas Taisutbas Teefas mahzijee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es turrefschu tawus Eik \nmus/ ne atstahj mann tik toht\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka turrehs weens Jaune \nlis fawu Zelfu Schkihstu? fo \nwinsch turrah̃ pehz tawee \nWahrdein.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es mehleju teiw no wisfe \nmannas Sir̃ds/ ne krezmann \ntaweeem Bausleem nomaldiht.\n"
    }
  ],
